Selection - Sergei

Snapshot of selection analysis output

p: p-value for non-neutrality (positve if alpha < beta, negative otherwise)

alpha : site MLE estimate for the synonymous rate

beta : site MLE estimate for the non-synonymous rate

T_int: total length of internal branches in the gene tree used for inference (subs/site)

T_total: total length of all branches in the gene tree used for inference (subs/site)
